title: Bob Dylan & Others All That Folk
description:
Bob Dylan was inspired by several different styles in his long career as folk, country, 
rock & roll, jazz, gospel,reggae and blues.And he inspired other artists in their music....

This 4 cd selection has the spot on the Folk influences

A www.dylannl.blogspot.com production. Artwork DylanForeverman France...

Also available All That Jazz, All That Blues, All That Reggae , All That Country, All That Gospel, All That Rock 'n Roll.....
